@20287 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20288 = ~Follow your new queen, Kiaransalee, the Vengeful Banshee~
@20289 = ~I was inducted into the cult of Kiaransalee, a deity of undeath. My mentor during the conversion was Narthuul Hollow Maw, a glabrezu disfigured by our Lady's nemesis. My goal is to spread death and chaos. I am to face a test in the future. I had better be ready.~
@20290 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20291 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20292 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20293 = ~Reunite the pair of bone earrings and return them to Ulfbrand in Ysgard~
@20294 = ~Ulfbrand gave me his earring in exchange for a promise that I will find the other one and return them both. Should I fail, the wrath of the entire Debt Collection Division will be upon me. I do not know if I will have a chance to return to Ysgard, where Ulfbrand is waiting for me, but the missing earring should be just on the other side of the portal, so I might as well take it with me.~
@20295 = ~I found the lost earring. I was right to assume it would be in the possession of one of the wererat thieves. I still do not know if I will have a chance to return to Ysgard, where Ulfbrand is waiting for me, but I have now completed the set, so I can return it to him if possible.~
@20296 = ~XXX~
@20298 = ~To repair his device for slime research, Pabeshts needs a shard from Lothar's lost golem, which is supposedly located somewhere by the Knife on the River. To reach it, I will need a boat with a skilled navigator. I am sure the captain on the beach and his monodrone will be able to help me.~
@20299 = ~I found the Knife in the River, but there is no sign of a golem underwater here. A chatty rat told me that a mad wizard sometimes flies out of the pipe sticking out of the ground. Maybe he has something to do with the golem's disappearance. Unfortunately, the pipe is practically vertical. I need a sturdy rope to get inside.~
@20300 = ~I obtained a rope used for tying up snakes. It is said to be very strong. I can use it to reach the pipe near the Knife in the River and search for the missing golem for Pabeshts.~
@20301 = ~I found the golem. It was hidden in a laboratory full of traps. The owner is not at home. I can now try to take a piece of the golem's body and deliver it to Pabeshts.~
@20302 = ~I managed to obtain a fragment of Lothar's golem. Now I have to deliver it to Suicide Falls so that Pabeshts can repair his magical device.~
@20303 = ~I managed to obtain a fragment of Lothar's golem. Now I have to deliver it to Suicide Falls so that Pabeshts can repair his magical device. I also freed the golem from captivity. It will likely return to the Bones of the Night now.~
@20304 = ~Find your true taste in art.~
@20305 = ~I left Haer'Dalis' head with Elvra at the Styx Oarsman. He will send it to a friend back home, a renowned pickle master. I imagine it will return delicious. I should find Elvra when I return from the Hells.~
@20306 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20307 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20308 = ~Rezerwacja~
@20309 = ~Rezerwacja~